{% doc %}
    Renders a secure strap snippet for faq item.
{% enddoc %}
<div class="secure-strap">
    <div class="secure-strap__item">
        <img src="https://qureskincaredns.com/sections/isolated/faqs/images/sec_strap_1.webp" alt="Secure strap" />
        <p>To secure your strap, first position the mask so the LED lights face towards you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="secure-strap__item">
        <img src="https://qureskincaredns.com/sections/isolated/faqs/images/sec_strap_2.webp" alt="Secure strap step 1" />
        <p><strong>Step 1.</strong> Slide the strap through clip 2, making sure the Qure logos on the strap are facing down.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="secure-strap__item">
        <img src="https://qureskincaredns.com/sections/isolated/faqs/images/sec_strap_3.webp" alt="Secure strap step 2" />
        <p><strong>Step 2.</strong> Insert the strap through the slide adjuster. You could now see the Qure logos on the strap.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="secure-strap__item">
        <img src="https://qureskincaredns.com/sections/isolated/faqs/images/sec_strap_4.webp" alt="Secure strap step 3" />
        <p><strong>Step 3.</strong> Slide the strap through clip 1, push the provided pin through the end of the strap, and secure the pin by pulling on the strap.</p>
    </div>
</div>